overview: “Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 16” is here! Filled with insane infomercials, local TV commercials, public access weirdness, music from The Animals, Echo & the Bunnymen, Royal Trux & 2, count ‘em 2 music videos from that maniacally melodic religious cult The Family International aka The Children of God, a rare TV appearance from Jean-Michel Basquiat, a classic appearance of Penn & Teller on Late Night with David Letterman, enough Satan & Jesus to shake a stick at, and more, more, more!!
title: Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 16
